OL,3,CCampaigners say new laws will help in
OL,4,Cfight against spiking
OL,6,FCampaigners are welcoming news that
OL,7,Fspiking someone's drink will be made a
OL,8,Fspecific criminal offence.
OL,10,FIt was one of a raft of measures
OL,11,Foutlined by the government in the
OL,12,FKing's Speech on 17 July.
OL,14,FDawn Dines is the CEO and Founder of
OL,15,FStamp out Spiking, which is based in
OL,16,FExeter, Devon.
