OL,3,CCampaigners say new laws will help in
OL,4,Cfight against spiking
OL,6,F"Keir Starmer's office said that
OL,7,Fthey're going to make this specific
OL,8,Foffence, so that's what we're hoping
OL,9,Ffor. Myself and my team will be here
OL,10,Fto make sure that that actually gets
OL,11,Fthrough."
OL,13,FMs Dines said she hopes the changes in
OL,14,Fthe law will see more offenders being
OL,15,Fprosecuted. She added: "What it will
OL,16,Fmean in reality is zero tolerance on
OL,17,Fspiking.
