OL,3,CCampaigners say new laws will help in
OL,4,Cfight against spiking
OL,6,FMs Dines said the fight against
OL,7,Fspiking isn't just confined to
OL,8,Fchanging the law and she is hoping for
OL,9,Fmore action to eradicate the problem.
OL,11,FShe said: "We're going to be looking
OL,12,Fat the government to put some funding
OL,13,Fin so we can train door supervisors,
OL,14,Fbar staff, security staff, street
OL,15,Fpastors, even public transport,
OL,16,Fbecause when these victims get spiked,
OL,17,Fsomebody's got to get them somewhere.
