OL,3,CCampaigners say new laws will help in
OL,4,Cfight against spiking
OL,6,F"So we all need everybody to be
OL,7,Fsinging off the same hymn sheet to
OL,8,Fmake sure that we are going to
OL,9,Fsafeguard as many people as possible
OL,10,Fin the future.
OL,12,F"After fighting for 20 years and all
OL,13,Fthe victims, men and women who broke
OL,14,Fdown in my arms and told me the most
OL,15,Fhorrific stories, for them I'm just
OL,16,Fdelighted."
